title: Brains and Eggs
description: Four aliens have taken on the human form and traveled to Earth in order to find out how humans live and what they do.

title: Post-Nasal Dick
description: Tommy kisses a girl, catches a bug and the whole crew gets ill.

title: Dick's First Birthday
description: For the first time, Dick gets confronted with his age when he's introduced to the concept of birthdays.

title: Dick Is from Mars, Sally Is from Venus
description: Sally has her very first date and Tommy starts going to high school.

title: Dick, Smoker
description: Dick takes up smoking and meanwhile Sally doesn't like to be overruled by Dick all the time.

title: Green-Eyed Dick
description: An old boyfriend of Dr. Albright shows up and Dick experiences what jealousy is.

title: Lonely Dick
description: Dick feels very lonely because Dr. Albright is on holiday.

title: Body & Soul & Dick
description: An obnoxious professor dies and his will says he wants Dick to speak at his funeral.

title: Ab-dick-ted
description: Dick doesn't want the family to always irritate each other and thinks they can learn from observing Dr. Albright and her brother Roy.

title: Truth or Dick
description: Dick finds out people sometimes lie to get what they want and Sally and Harry find out how hard it is to get a driver's license.

title: The Art of Dick
description: After failing everything he has tried so far, Harry turns out to be a good painter.

title: Frozen Dick
description: The Solomons have their first experience with snow and act appropriately, or so they think.

title: Angry Dick
description: Dick wants the Solomons to meet the neighbors.

title: The Dicks They Are A-Changin'
description: Dr. Albright thinks Dick is actually an activist she met in the 1960's.

title: I Enjoy Being a Dick
description: Sally and Harry get a job and Dick feels kept out when he can't come to Dr. Albright and Nina's women-only study group.

title: Dick Like Me
description: The Solomons come to realize they don't belong to any ethnic group.

title: Assault with a Deadly Dick
description: The Solomons' car radio is stolen and Dick is being robbed.

title: Father Knows Dick
description: Harry acts upset and even a bit rebellious and Dick figures Harry needs a father figure.

title: Selfish Dick
description: Dick is devastated when Dr. Albright gets a new office.

title: See Dick Run
description: Mary has finally agreed to go on a date with Dick.

roles.char: Guy Who Chokes on a Shrimp

title: See Dick Continue to Run: Part 1
description: Sally, Harry and Tommy experience Dick's replacement is very aggravating while they don't know Dick is still trapped in the basement.

title: See Dick Continue to Run: Part 2
description: The Solomons have freed Dick and now he's after his replacement.

title: Hotel Dick
description: Dick feels he has to tell Mary he's an alien.

title: Big Angry Virgin from Outer Space
description: Sally and Mr. Randall are having a conflict and August tests Tommy's loyalty to her.

title: Much Ado About Dick
description: Mary doesn't want everybody to know she and Dick have a relationship, which Dick doesn't understand.

title: Dick the Vote
description: Harry runs for city council after he's mistaken for an activist.

title: Fourth and Dick
description: It's homecoming weekend and everybody is excited about the game, except for Dick.

title: World's Greatest Dick
description: Against Tommy's will, Dick enlists him in a school for gifted students.

title: My Mother the Alien
description: Mrs. Dubcek asks the Solomons to babysit her grandson.

title: Gobble, Gobble, Dick, Dick
description: It's Thanksgiving. Unfortunately, the Solomons don't have a clue what Thanksgiving is.

title: Dick Jokes
description: Dick desperately tries to find out how he can be funny.

title: Jolly Old St. Dick
description: The Solomons experience their first Christmas.

title: Proud Dick
description: Dick quits his job at the university and Harry loses his memory.

title: Romeo & Juliet & Dick
description: Dick directs a school play Tommy wants to be in, but makes him the prop guy.

title: Guilty as Dick
description: Dick sprains his ankle while he's doing Mary a favor and she feels guilty.

title: A Dick on One Knee
description: Sally meets Michel, a cute French guy who asks her to marry him.

title: Same Old Song and Dick
description: Dick feels his relationship with Mary is in a rut.

title: I Brake for Dick
description: Dick has run over a chipmunk and he starts to ban everything that's made of animals.

title: Dick Behaving Badly
description: Harry learns Dick how to become a real man so he won't be whipped by Mary anymore.

title: Dickmalion
description: With Dick's help, Mary gets the opportunity to get in with Rutherford's high society.

title: Sensitive Dick
description: Dick has to take sensitivity classes and Harry's fling Vicki is back.

title: Will Work for Dick
description: When an offended Nina quits as Dick's secretary, he gives Harry the job.

title: Fifteen Minutes of Dick
description: Sally stands up to Mark Hamill who unknowingly has taken the Solomons place in a restaurant and becomes a local hero.

title: Dick and the Single Girl
description: A smart and shy librarian at school is attracted to Dick.

title: A Nightmare on Dick Street: Part 1
description: Dick experiences his first nightmare and the Solomons think he's gone mad.

title: A Nightmare on Dick Street: Part 2
description: Dick and Sally are sober again and are informed they are all going back to the home planet for emergency maintenance.

title: Fun with Dick and Janet: Part 1
description: Sally, Harry & Tommy return, along with a wife for Dick selected by the Big Giant Head, Jane, his niece.

title: Fun with Dick and Janet: Part 2
description: Dick proposes. Mary disposes.

title: Tricky Dick
description: Out of frustration over their break-up, Dick and Mary start a series of very childish practical jokes.

title: Dick-In-Law
description: Dick accompanies Mary on a trip to her parents, who still think Mary and Dick are a couple.

title: Scaredy Dick
description: Dick has to get a medical check up but doesn't want to go because he's scared.

title: Moby Dick
description: Dick has gained quite some weight since the break-up with Mary.

title: Eleven Angry Men and One Dick
description: Dick has jury duty. Sally meets dark and intriguing Seth.

title: A Friend in Dick
description: Dick has to find somebody to take to a dance performance and realizes he doesn't have any friends.

title: Seven Deadly Clips
description: With the seven deadly sins as a guide, the Solomons reflect on their adventures on earth so far.

title: Tom, Dick and Mary
description: Sally finds a job while Tommy and Dick are competing over Mary.

title: Jailhouse Dick
description: Dick takes care of a felon because he feels he can make an honest man out of him.

title: Dick on a Roll
description: Dick ends up in a wheelchair while Harry is unhappy with Vicki being celibate.

title: The Great Dickdater
description: Dick is ready to start dating again and Tommy and Harry find a wallet.

title: 36! 24! 36! Dick!: Part 1
description: Rutherford gets swamped with gorgeous women.

title: 36! 24! 36! Dick!: Part 2
description: Dick, Tommy and Harry have to save Sally, and the entire world, from the Venusian women.

title: Pickles and Ice Cream
description: Harry's pet dog from the home planet has somehow made it to Rutherford, in human form. Sally pretends to be pregnant.

title: Auto Eurodicka
description: Dick discovers casual sex while Sally desperately wants to buy a very expensive car.

title: Portrait of Tommy as an Old Man
description: Tommy is tired of being treated like a kid and decides to retire. Officer Don accidentally steals one of Sally's panties.

title: Stuck with Dick
description: Dick tries to get Mary back and considers himself lucky when the two of them get locked in the school library overnight.

title: My Daddy's Little Girl
description: Mary's father George has left his wife, again, and gets along well with Sally. Very well indeed.

title: The Physics of Being Dick
description: Dick tells Sally and Harry to get a job while he wants to become a cop.

title: Just Your Average Dick
description: After August and Mary admit they can be pretty weird sometimes, the Solomons decide to become totally average.

title: Dick and the Other Guy
description: Dick competes with new professor Dr. Neesam over Mary. Sally thinks Don isn't interested in her anymore.

title: Sally and Don's First Kiss
description: It's time for Don and Sally's first kiss, Harry has his night school exam and the cafeteria lady hates Dick.

title: When Aliens Camp
description: Dick decides the Solomons go camping, tells them not to bring anyone else because it's a family weekend and then invites Mary to come along.

title: The Tooth Harry
description: Dick wants a part in a university promotional video, Harry takes Nina to the dentist and Don gives Sally a key to his house.

title: Eat, Drink, Dick, Mary
description: Dick plans a romantic dinner as an anniversary for him and Mary and everybody is invited.

title: Dr. Solomon's Traveling Alien Show
description: Harry has been kidnapped and the Solomons try to find him, a task that is complicated by the fact that Dick is literally losing his mind.

title: Power Mad Dick
description: Mary is the new dean and Dick thinks this gives him power as well. Sally has lost her virginity.

title: Feelin' Albright
description: When Sally realizes Don had other girlfriends before her, she considers them competition and wants to know who she's up against.

title: Collect Call for Dick
description: Starting as a promotional giveaway at Rusty's Burgers, Dick becomes addicted to collecting Fuzzy Buddies dolls at all cost. Tommy is forced by the basketball coach to show pep by dressing up as Hootie the mascot.

title: What's Love Got to Do, Got to Do with Dick?
description: Sally tries to fix Nina up with Eric, a colleague of Don. Dick finds himself attracted to Jennifer, his new office mate.

title: I Am Dick Pentameter!
description: Dick is fascinated by Jennifer, his new office mate, and suggests to Mary they should see other people. To his surprise, she agrees.

title: D3: Judgment Day
description: Dick wants to break up with Jennifer. Don has asked Sally to go bowling but Sally hasn't got a clue what bowling is.

title: Indecent Dick
description: Sally tries out for a nude photo shoot for an adult magazine at Pendelton State University over the objections of boyfriend Don. Harry tries out home nudism and believes clothing might be a scam. An enraged Dick tracks down a photographer who took nude pictures of Dr. Mary Albright twenty years ago but then has a change of heart. Tommy becomes enamored with a new lab partner.

title: Happy New Dick!
description: Tommy organizes a new year party at the bar where Harry works while Dick feels he hasn't accomplished anything the past year.

title: Two-Faced Dick
description: After three years, the Big Giant Head has granted Sally's request to be a man and switches Sally and Dick's bodies.

title: Dick Solomon of the Indiana Solomons
description: Dick receives an invitation for a family reunion that was meant for someone else but the Solomons go anyway.

title: Dick and Taxes
description: When they lie on their IRS form, the Solomons receive an audit notice and fear the IRS will discover they're aliens.

title: Sally Forth
description: While Dick is in a feud with the Dubceks, Don asks Sally to marry him.

title: Paranoid Dick
description: Dick convinces Mary there's a conspiracy against her at the university.

title: The House That Dick Built
description: Sally moves out while Harry and Vicki are considering having a baby.

title: Superstitious Dick
description: Dick and Mary both receive a chain letter. Mary throws hers away and a lot of bad luck befalls her.

title: Y2dicK
description: Dick discovers computers and gets hooked.

title: Dick 'The Mouth' Solomon
description: Sally meets Italian-American Sammy Marchetti, who's also known as 'the Butcher'. Mary & Dick and Harry & Vicki go to a couple's retreat.

title: Citizen Solomon
description: The Solomons hire a maid now that Sally has moved out. Tommy becomes editor-in-chief of the school paper.

title: Alien Hunter
description: Birthday boy Dick meets a woman, Charlotte, who's very interested in him.

title: Dick v. Strudwick
description: Strudwick, a colleague of Dick, has written a physics book that everyone considers to be brilliant, which makes Dick very jealous.

title: Near Dick Experience
description: Tommy, Harry and Sally had a near death experience and appreciate the world like never before. A jealous Dick wants to experience this too.

title: Dick's Big Giant Headache: Part 1
description: The Big Giant Head comes to Earth.

title: Dick's Big Giant Headache: Part 2
description: The Big Giant Head continues to behave ill-mannered, inappropriate and unadapted.

title: Episode I: The Baby Menace
description: It's a boy! It's a girl! It's an alien? The alien baby!

title: Dick for Tat
description: When a drunk Mary tells him she once had a fling with Strudwick, Dick wants to get even with Strudwick by sleeping with his wife.

title: The Fifth Solomon
description: Dick wrecks the car and, to their surprise, the Solomons miss the car and feel sentimental about it.

title: Dial M for Dick
description: Mary invites the Solomons to a murder mystery weekend. However, the Solomons don't know it's not real.

title: Dick and Tuck
description: Dick considers undergoing plastic surgery.

title: Dick, Who's Coming to Dinner
description: The Solomons learn about racism.

title: Sex and the Sally
description: Dick learns about tipping while Sally learns sex can lead to pregnancy.

title: Charitable Dick
description: Dick discovers charity when he and Mary go to a charity auction. Don can't sleep because Sally snores.

title: The Loud Solomon Family: A Dickumentary
description: Mary wants to make a documentary about the Solomons.

title: Gwen, Larry, Dick and Mary
description: Mary suggests she and Dick should spend time with another couple. Tommy, Harry and Sally discover the laundromat.

title: Dick Puts the 'Id' in Cupid
description: Tommy hopes to lose his virginity to Alissa on Valentine's Day.

title: The Big Giant Head Returns
description: The Big Giant Head returns to take his son with him to the home planet.

title: Rutherford Beauty
description: Dick has erotic fantasies about Nina. Sally is under the spell of a cooking expert a la

title: This Little Dick Went to Market
description: Dick and Tommy go into business and buy shares. Sally feels her position as the toughest chick is threatened by Janice, the new, tough and strong rookie cop.

title: Youth Is Wasted on the Dick
description: Don and a few colleagues settle in the Solomons' house because they suspect there's a video pirate in the neighborhood. Dick wants to know what it's like to be young.

title: Dick Strikes Out
description: A new chancellor arrives at Pendleton and his plans make Dick decide to organize a strike.

title: Shall We Dick?
description: Sally and Alissa become friends, much to the chagrin of Don and Tommy. Dick and Mary enter a dance contest, despite the fact Mary can't dance.

title: Dick and Harry Fall Down a Hole
description: Dick and Harry fall down a hole. A hole expert is hired to get them out.

title: Frankie Goes to Rutherford
description: Because of a misunderstanding, Frank, a former student of Mary who's gay, thinks Dick is gay too and takes him to a gay bar.

title: Dick Solomon's Day Off
description: Dick finds out what sick days are and what one can use them for. Harry, Sally and Tommy listen to cellphone conversations on Don's scanner.

title: The Big Giant Head Returns Again: Part 1
description: Sally thinks Alissa wants to dump Tommy, Harry wants to ask Janice out and the Big Giant Head (visiting Earth once again) admits his marriage is troubled.

title: The Big Giant Head Returns Again: Part 2
description: Dick tells the others The Big Giant Head is his father and Tommy finds out Sally dumped Alissa on his behalf.

title: Les Liaisons Dickgereuses
description: To Mary's chagrin, her rich sister Renata visits and Dick thinks up a plan to punish her for the grief she caused Mary. Sally and Harry start a youth center in the Solomon's living room.

title: Fear and Loathing in Rutherford
description: Can Harry and Sally scare up a date for Tommy?

title: InDickscretion
description: Inspired by

title: Dick'll Take Manhattan: Part 1
description: Out of boredom, Dick, Sally and Harry go to a parallel universe and end up in New York where they all live the good life.

title: Dick'll Take Manhattan: Part 2
description: Start spreading the news, the Solomons are in New York City!

title: Why Dickie Can't Teach
description: Sally is stunned to find Rutherford's 10 most powerful men don't include her beau, Officer Don. With Tommy about to matriculate, Sally focuses her alien super powers on getting Don to be the man she can be the great woman behind. Dick can't bear for Tommy to go away for university, so he pushes to lure him to the local clown college, where Dick teaches. Commander Dick can't admit his empty nest anxiety, so he stresses the diploma mill's advantages, like his fabulous teaching.

title: B.D.O.C.
description: Tommy goes away to college, causing Dick extreme parental withdrawal. Meanwhile, Sally & Harry interview potential replacements, and Sally hires a "pretty boy" to be the new information officer.

title: Red, White & Dick
description: Dick loves America, but does America love Dick?

title: Dick Digs
description: Sally, Harry and Tommy rent out Dick's room, while Dick and Mary are away on an archaeological dig, where Mary is disappointed to come up empty after Dick finds a "pointy rock".

title: There's No Business Like Dick Business
description: Mary has her purse snatched in a park, so Harry, Nina and Mary attend a self defense course that Don is teaching. Dick and Sally become a nightclub magician and a glamorous assistant.

title: A Dick Replacement
description: It's double trouble as Dick searches for his own replacement.

title: Dick's Ark
description: Sally gets a job doing TV weather. Dick gives little respect to Mary's wish to spend some time apart.

title: You Don't Know Dick
description: When it comes to Mary, Dick doesn't know squat.

title: My Mother, My Dick
description: Mother of Mary. Dick takes on Mary's scary mom.

title: Glengarry Glen Dick
description: Dick and Don share the cost of a timeshare. Sally discovers Tommy has grown taller than Harry.

title: Dick Soup for the Soul
description: When Tommy rushes a frat, Pledge Master Sally turns up the heat!

title: Mary Loves Scoochie: Part 1
description: A rival for Mary's love challenges Dick to a deadly duel.

title: Mary Loves Scoochie: Part 2
description: Liam Neesam's out to destroy the world. Can Dick stop him?

title: The Thing That Wouldn't Die: Part 1
description: Having witnessed Dick's alien encounter with Liam Neeson; Mary requires an explanation. The "Big Giant Head" delivers some disturbing news.

title: The Thing That Wouldn't Die: Part 2
description: Elvis Costello entertains at the Solomon's going away party.
